### 1. Send Command (User -> Cloud)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/command/dev-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type": "watering_mode",
    "value": "high"
}

### 2. Send Telemetry (Device -> Cloud)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/telemetry/dev-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "battery": 92,
    "status": "online"
}